		dependsOn: ["mt-tenant-model", "mt-visibility-model", "mt-identity-and-authorization", "mt-data-sharing-patterns", "mt-agent-tenant-scope", "mt-tenant-isolation-testing", "mt-org-lifecycle", "mt-audit-and-compliance-trail"]
		rationale: "Multi-tenancy degrades with feature additions: new table without RLS, new endpoint without projection, new agent without scoping. Quarterly review + CI isolation tests + production monitoring: continuous proof of isolation."
